headline: Canada Trucker TFI Reverses Plan to Incorporate in the U.S.
summary: The Montreal company said the change was based on feedback from shareholders, among them Quebec’s Caisse de Dépôt.

headline: FactSet Research: The Facts Look A Lot Better
